data.title: old — PT Day of Service
data.meta_description: PT Day of Service, PTDOS, relies on ambassadors to organize service sites, recruit volunteers and spread the word about the day. Ambassadors can act alone in their community, or can serve on behalf of their organization. Ambassadors should sign up in the pledge form
data.text:
2015 Ambassadors: The heart of PTDOS

Thank you to our 417 Ambassadors from across the world! Each ambassador led a service project, recruited other participants, and reported their outcomes. PTDOS would not have been possible without their extraordinary efforts!

Make sure to check out our gallery to see many of their incredible acts of service.
